 E(K,1) = 1+\frac1{1-1/K}+\frac1{(1-1/K)(1-2/K)}+\ldots + \frac1{(1-1/K)(1-2/K)\cdots(1-(K-1)/K)}\\= 1+\frac K{K-1} +\frac{K^2}{(K-1)(K-2)}+\ldots +\frac{K^{K-1}}{(K-1)!}\\=\sum_{r=0}^K\frac{K^{K-r}r!}{K!}
